narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, take if you're interested in the material

Yes! You go in having no real understanding of the legal system and leave with a solid understanding and a bunch of cases you can't help but bring up all the time because they're just so interesting. The workload is also very manageable -- Joyce is really sensitive to that. She also got really great guest speakers! Long and the short of it is take the class!
I would not recommend to another student. Class itself was really not enjoyable.
